“Russia” is led by Anatoly Aksakov, known for his scrupulousness in everything concerning the interests of banks and their clients; a first-rate professional who is highly regarded at the Central Bank: virtually the entire leadership of the Central Bank attends the association’s annual events, and all of the regulator’s relevant legislative initiatives go through the expert evaluations of the “regionals”.
